Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.99,0:00:22.75,Watamote-Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(3562,1)}Kiss Him, Not Me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.86,0:01:33.86,Watamote-Ep_Title,,0000,0000,0000,,Christmas in the {\c&H5DEEF5&}Holy{\c&HFFFFFF&} Land
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.66,0:01:39.70,Default,Nanashima,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do a Chri-Pa, guys! A Chri-Pa!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.08,0:01:40.86,Default,All,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.20,0:01:43.85,Default,Nanashima,0000,0000,0000,,A Chri-Pa! You know, Christmas party!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.85,0:01:45.08,Default,Igarashi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. Sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.08,0:01:47.71,Default,Nanashima,0000,0000,0000,,Right? We can reserve\N a karaoke room or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.71,0:01:48.83,Default,Nanashima,0000,0000,0000,,Does Christmas Eve work?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.83,0:01:49.50,Default,Igarashi,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.50,0:01:50.49,Default,Shinomiya,0000,0000,0000,,It works for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.49,0:01:51.35,Default,Mutsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Same.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.62,0:01:53.63,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,Um, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.63,0:01:56.51,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to Comiket on \NChristmas Eve, so I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.66,0:01:57.68,Default,Boys,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.97,0:02:00.22,Default,Nanashima,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! It's Christmas Eve!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.22,0:02:02.55,Default,Nanashima,0000,0000,0000,,It's the day everyone looks\N forward to the most!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.55,0:02:06.47,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me about it! It somehow \Nfell on the same day this year!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.47,0:02:08.28,Default,Nanashima,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what I mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.28,0:02:10.35,Default,Nanashima,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, what is Comiket anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.61,0:02:14.73,Default,Shinomiya,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently it's the country's \Nlargest doujinshi exhibition sale.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.73,0:02:17.72,Default,Igarashi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. You said you went during \Nsummer break, too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.72,0:02:18.42,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.00,0:02:22.18,Default,Nanashima,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell? If you went over \Nsummer, isn't that enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.18,0:02:25.45,Default,Nanashima,0000,0000,0000,,Christmas Eve only comes once\N a year! A perfect end to the year!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.60,0:02:30.46,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, but my year isn't \Ncomplete until I attend Comiket!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.59,0:02:33.46,sign_7066_26_Shi,left,0000,0000,0000,,Shi
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.59,0:02:33.46,sign_7066_27_Nana,Mid,0000,0000,0000,,Nana
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.59,0:02:33.46,sign_7066_28_Iga,right,0000,0000,0000,,Iga
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.75,0:02:33.46,Watamote-internal/narrator,all,0000,0000,0000,,S-She's made up her mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.50,0:02:38.96,Default,Mutsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, look. There's a history \Nstudy group there, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.96,0:02:40.60,Default,Mutsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.60,0:02:42.30,Default,Mutsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.50,0:02:44.97,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! It's super fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.20,0:02:48.16,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,These days, there's more there \Nthan just manga and anime.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.16,0:02:51.89,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,It's spread to other genres, \Ntoo! Like songwriting and foreign dramas!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.89,0:02:54.73,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see them all!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.23,0:02:55.98,Default,Mutsumi,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.98,0:02:57.54,Default,Mutsumi,0000,0000,0000,,How about we all go?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.54,0:03:00.57,Default,Mutsumi,0000,0000,0000,,That way, we can close out the \Nyear and have a party, all at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.79,0:03:03.63,Watamote-internal/narrator,Boys,0000,0000,0000,,Th-There goes that airhead again!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.63,0:03:06.32,Default,Mutsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but Serinuma-san, were you \Nalready going with someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.32,0:03:07.37,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.60,0:03:11.00,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,The friend I always go with has plans,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.37,0:03:13.25,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,so I'm going alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.61,0:03:16.50,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,If you could all make it, I'd be overjoyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.74,0:03:17.65,Watamote-internal/narrator,Igarashi,0000,0000,0000,,Overjoyed...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.65,0:03:18.58,Watamote-internal/narrator,Nanashima,0000,0000,0000,,Overjoyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.58,0:03:19.51,Watamote-internal/narrator,Shinomiya,0000,0000,0000,,Overjoyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.95,0:03:23.62,Default,Igarashi,0000,0000,0000,,All right. We'll go to Comiket, \Nand have a party on the way home!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.62,0:03:24.39,Default,Igarashi,0000,0000,0000,,Sound good?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.36,0:03:26.80,Default,All,0000,0000,0000,,No objections here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.14,0:03:30.68,sign_8761_52_December_24th__E,sign,0000,0000,0000,,December 24th: Early Morning, Christmas Eve
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.18,0:03:30.68,sign_8792_53_Takami_Station,station,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1362,1)}Takami Station
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.74,0:03:34.86,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.33,0:03:37.40,Default,All,0000,0000,0000,,G-Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.79,0:03:39.60,Default,Igarashi,0000,0000,0000,,Why are we meeting so early?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.60,0:03:41.21,Default,Nanashima,0000,0000,0000,,I woke up at 5 A.M.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.21,0:03:43.65,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,If we don't go early, all \Nthe books will be gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.65,0:03:44.78,Default,Shinomiya,0000,0000,0000,,So sleepy...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.93,0:03:47.28,sign_9294_60_Guide_to_Comiket,title,0000,0000,0000,,Guide to {\c&H996DA3&}Comiket
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.93,0:03:49.12,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! This guide has what you need \Nto know, like proper etiquette and history.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.12,0:03:51.03,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,So make sure to read it on the train.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.03,0:03:53.21,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,Onward! To the holy land!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.55,0:03:56.27,Default,Shinomiya,0000,0000,0000,,We might be the first on board.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.66,0:03:59.92,Default,Nanashima,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry up and buy books so \Nwe can come back and party after.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.04,0:04:03.05,sign_9747_66_Kokusai_tenjijo_,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Kokusai-tenjijo Station
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.29,0:04:03.99,Default,Nanashima,0000,0000,0000,,Wha...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.66,0:04:07.43,Default,Nanashima,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with this crowd?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.34,0:04:11.93,Default,Nanashima,0000,0000,0000,,Are all these people going to Comiket?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.93,0:04:13.64,Default,Igarashi,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.64,0:04:15.40,Default,Shinomiya,0000,0000,0000,,It's still only seven in the morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.62,0:04:18.57,Default,Nanashima,0000,0000,0000,,The train was packed,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.08,0:04:20.99,Default,Nanashima,0000,0000,0000,,and the platform had so many people...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.38,0:04:24.03,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Here! Don't push! Don't \Nforce the doors open!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.03,0:04:25.46,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Don't throw away your hope!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.46,0:04:28.24,Default,Shinomiya,0000,0000,0000,,The staff workers are screaming like crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.51,0:04:30.24,Default,All,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck is all this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.51,0:04:30.24,sign_10600_78_Mu,left,0000,0000,0000,,Mu
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.51,0:04:30.24,sign_10600_79_Nana,left mid,0000,0000,0000,,Nana
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.51,0:04:30.24,sign_10600_80_Shi,right mid,0000,0000,0000,,Shi
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.51,0:04:30.24,sign_10600_81_Iga,right,0000,0000,0000,,Iga
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.43,0:04:34.16,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if it's because it's Christmas Eve.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.16,0:04:36.42,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,I think there's fewer people \Nthis year than last...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.39,0:04:38.64,Default,Nanashima,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.64,0:04:39.92,Default,Shinomiya,0000,0000,0000,,...fewer people?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.91,0:04:43.30,Default,Igarashi,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon! We don't wanna get separated.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.43,0:04:46.30,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Those in general admittance, \Nplease come this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.55,0:04:48.77,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,We'll wait here until the doors open.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.77,0:04:50.18,Default,Igarashi,0000,0000,0000,,At 10, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.41,0:04:52.68,Default,Igarashi,0000,0000,0000,,And it's 7:30 right now, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.95,0:04:55.49,Default,boys,0000,0000,0000,,T-Two and a half hours?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.93,0:04:58.57,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right! Here, take these!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.01,0:05:03.20,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,Waiting out here will get cold, \Nso feel free to use them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.31,0:05:05.52,Default,Mutsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.52,0:05:06.34,Watamote-internal/narrator,Igarashi,0000,0000,0000,,We can wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.14,0:05:08.21,sign_11728_96_Ba_dump,text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,300)}Ba-dump
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.34,0:05:07.59,Watamote-internal/narrator,Shinomiya,0000,0000,0000,,Two and a half hours...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.59,0:05:09.03,Watamote-internal/narrator,Nanashima,0000,0000,0000,,...is a cinch!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.03,0:05:11.37,Watamote-internal/narrator,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,But little did they know...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.18,0:05:16.96,sign_11819_100_Plus_one_hour,text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(420,5941)}Plus {\c&HDA3CB1&}One{\c} Hour
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.37,0:05:14.08,Watamote-internal/narrator,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,After the doors opened,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.46,0:05:17.08,Watamote-internal/narrator,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,there'd be another hour \Nbefore they could enter.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.66,0:05:21.96,sign_12164_103_Exhausted,text,0000,0000,0000,,Exhausted
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.07,0:05:23.73,Default,Mutsumi,0000,0000,0000,,All right, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.73,0:05:26.97,Default,Mutsumi,0000,0000,0000,,As we discussed, let's split into three \Ngroups and finish this shopping list.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.27,0:05:29.92,Watamote-internal/narrator,Boys,0000,0000,0000,,What an incredibly thorough map!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.18,0:05:34.89,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really all right \Nwith helping me shop?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.18,0:05:37.92,Default,Igarashi,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we don't have anything \Nwe want for ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.92,0:05:40.17,Default,Igarashi,0000,0000,0000,,We can get everything faster if we split up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.78,0:05:43.53,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks. I really appreciate it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.60,0:05:54.74,Watamote-internal/narrator,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, thank you so much for helping \Nme out, even though I'm acting so selfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.74,0:05:55.79,Watamote-internal/narrator,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,And also...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.01,0:05:57.17,Watamote-internal/narrator,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.91,0:06:03.64,Watamote-internal/narrator,Nanashima,0000,0000,0000,,Right. The stuff she wants is BL.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.46,0:06:05.11,Watamote-overlap-top,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Two hot guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.64,0:06:06.22,Watamote-internal/narrator,Nanashima,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That, and I think these girls\N are picturing something funny.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.11,0:06:06.22,Watamote-overlap-top,Girl 2,0000,0000,0000,,Are they a couple?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.49,0:06:09.74,Default,Igarashi,0000,0000,0000,,Um, can we have the new issue \Nthat went on sale today?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.74,0:06:10.59,Default,Girl 2,0000,0000,0000,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.77,0:06:11.97,Watamote-internal/narrator,Nanashima,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.97,0:06:15.07,Watamote-internal/narrator,Nanashima,0000,0000,0000,,He's perfectly mastered that "this \Nis just for someone else" look!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.07,0:06:18.10,Watamote-internal/narrator,Igarashi,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Nana. You lose if you let \Nsomething like this get to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.32,0:06:20.35,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.56,0:06:22.94,Default,Igarashi,0000,0000,0000,,All right, Nana. Let's keep going like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.94,0:06:25.39,Default,Nanashima,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, yeah. The next one is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.39,0:06:27.53,Default,Nanashima,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? It's the next next booth over.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.53,0:06:29.63,Default,Igarashi,0000,0000,0000,,Um, the newest issue, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.63,0:06:30.24,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.50,0:06:32.28,Default,Nanashima,0000,0000,0000,,The next one's right here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.02,0:06:32.58,Watamote-overlap,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Please take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.28,0:06:33.29,Default,Nanashima,0000,0000,0000,,And the next one.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.58,0:06:34.24,Watamote-overlap,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.73,0:06:34.91,Default,Nanashima,0000,0000,0000,,Next.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.24,0:06:35.77,Watamote-overlap,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,We have a new issue.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.22,0:06:36.19,Default,Nanashima,0000,0000,0000,,Next.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.77,0:06:37.50,Watamote-overlap,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.96,0:06:40.42,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,It's like they're carpet bombing the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.97,0:06:42.68,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,They're doing the crab walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.68,0:06:44.35,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,They must love these comics.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.35,0:06:45.88,Watamote-internal/narrator,Both,0000,0000,0000,,We don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.55,0:06:50.29,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,Give me all the new issues!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.29,0:06:51.51,Default,Girls,0000,0000,0000,,Coming right up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.38,0:06:55.76,Default,Mutsumi,0000,0000,0000,,You're very skilled.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.98,0:06:58.13,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, uh, thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.13,0:07:00.72,Default,Mutsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Did you make this all by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.72,0:07:01.90,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.10,0:07:05.73,Default,Mutsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing. I can't draw,\Nso you have my respect.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.99,0:07:08.06,Watamote-internal/narrator,Girls,0000,0000,0000,,A-An angel!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.06,0:07:09.24,Watamote-internal/narrator,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,He's radiant!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.47,0:07:11.42,Default,Girls,0000,0000,0000,,My eyes! My eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.42,0:07:15.07,Default,Shinomiya,0000,0000,0000,,Come on! Enough with the idle \Nchatter! Let's get this over with!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.31,0:07:16.91,Default,Mutsumi,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't idle chatter.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.91,0:07:19.46,Default,Mutsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, it's a while before our meetup time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.67,0:07:23.11,Default,Shinomiya,0000,0000,0000,,I want to finish this up \Nquickly and get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.11,0:07:24.93,Default,Mutsimi,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Isn't this fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.93,0:07:25.95,Default,Shinomiya,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.19,0:07:30.42,Default,Shinomiya,0000,0000,0000,,There are too many people, the books are \Nheavy, it's cold outside, but hot inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.42,0:07:33.09,Default,Shinomiya,0000,0000,0000,,The place is dusty, too big, \Nand we're walking too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.35,0:07:34.62,Default,Shinomia,0000,0000,0000,,What's more...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.05,0:07:38.73,Default,Shinomiya,0000,0000,0000,,It feels like I could lose you at any second!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.73,0:07:39.84,Default,Mutsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.84,0:07:40.85,Default,Shinomiya,0000,0000,0000,,Are you a child?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.61,0:07:44.03,Default,Mutsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Then how about I try this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.97,0:07:48.55,Default,Mutsumi,0000,0000,0000,,You know what? After we're done, I'd \Nlike to go see the history study group.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.81,0:07:53.24,Default,Shinomiya,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose this is better \Nthan you getting lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.24,0:07:54.63,Default,Shinomiya,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.23,0:07:56.57,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.57,0:07:58.49,Default,Girl 2,0000,0000,0000,,Adorable!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.01,0:08:09.10,Watamote-internal/narrator,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,Look at this haul!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.44,0:08:11.67,Watamote-internal/narrator,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,Guess the others aren't here yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.87,0:08:13.97,Watamote-internal/narrator,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,We did say we were meeting at 2:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.87,0:08:18.62,Watamote-internal/narrator,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,I've gotta thank them all properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.62,0:08:20.39,Watamote-internal/narrator,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what would be good...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.07,0:08:29.07,Default,Cameraman,0000,0000,0000,,Nice, very nice! Can you strike a pose for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.07,0:08:32.84,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop! I'm not a cosplayer!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.84,0:08:34.71,Default,Cameraman,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, what a waste!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.71,0:08:36.86,Default,Cameraman,0000,0000,0000,,Just lemme take a few shots!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.04,0:08:41.25,Default,Cameraman,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.55,0:08:45.67,Default,Nishina,0000,0000,0000,,That's bad manners, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.66,0:08:51.30,Default,Nishina,0000,0000,0000,,Not a gentleman, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.71,0:08:54.04,Default,Cameraman,0000,0000,0000,,What's your problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.30,0:08:56.20,Default,Nishina,0000,0000,0000,,If you call yourself a photographer,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.20,0:08:58.18,Default,Nishina,0000,0000,0000,,shouldn't you carry yourself with decorum?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.65,0:09:01.81,Default,Nishina,0000,0000,0000,,It's not at all acceptable to take \Nphotos of a lady who refuses.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.15,0:09:04.52,Default,Nishina,0000,0000,0000,,You understand, don't you? Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.74,0:09:05.90,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,You're being rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.90,0:09:07.75,Default,Man 2,0000,0000,0000,,People like you give us a bad name!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.75,0:09:08.52,Default,Man 3,0000,0000,0000,,Apologize!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.82,0:09:11.51,Default,Nishina,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's upset with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.35,0:09:17.82,Watamote-overlap-top,Crowd,0000,0000,0000,,On your knees! On your knees!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.94,0:09:16.03,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.20,0:09:18.18,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.18,0:09:21.79,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're not going to do this \Nsort of thing again, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.79,0:09:24.54,Default,Cameraman,0000,0000,0000,,I-I get it! Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.07,0:09:29.29,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,That was a shock.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.60,0:09:32.43,Default,Nishina,0000,0000,0000,,You're letting him off with that? That's kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.27,0:09:34.58,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.80,0:09:38.38,Default,Nishina,0000,0000,0000,,Trouble-making punks like that crop \Nup from time to time. Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.71,0:09:44.40,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're Sebastian from {\i1}Gray Butler{\i0} right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.40,0:09:44.94,Default,Nishina,0000,0000,0000,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.94,0:09:48.54,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing! It's perfect! \NYou look just like him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.98,0:09:50.34,Default,Nishina,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.34,0:09:51.27,Default,Nanashima,0000,0000,0000,,There she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.56,0:09:53.28,Default,Nanashima,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. We got a bit lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.53,0:09:55.79,Default,Igarashi,0000,0000,0000,,Our phones had bad reception, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.79,0:09:57.15,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for all your hard work!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.53,0:10:00.73,Default,Nishina,0000,0000,0000,,What's this? You already \Nhave so many princes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.73,0:10:02.91,Default,Nishina,0000,0000,0000,,You guys should keep a better eye on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.75,0:10:05.41,Default,Nanashima,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.63,0:10:08.52,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well, he just helped me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.92,0:10:13.91,Default,Nishina,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, I'll leave the rest to your \Nprinces, and excuse myself, my lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.52,0:10:19.35,Default,Nishina,0000,0000,0000,,Adieu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.18,0:10:26.98,Default,Nanashima,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.19,0:10:29.41,Default,Igarashi,0000,0000,0000,,Serinuma-san, did he do anything to you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.41,0:10:31.43,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,N-N-No! That's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.43,0:10:34.99,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,I got tangled up with a creep \Nearlier and he helped me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.44,0:10:36.62,Default,Igarashi,0000,0000,0000,,Tangled?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.92,0:10:39.34,Default,Igarashi,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. If only we weren't so late...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.34,0:10:41.45,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it! Don't worry about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.72,0:10:44.14,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,You're the ones going along\N with my selfish whims.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.14,0:10:45.91,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who's sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.91,0:10:48.02,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,I really appreciate it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.02,0:10:48.90,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.93,0:10:54.44,Default,Nanashima,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Shall we party?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.44,0:10:55.30,Default,Igarashi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.30,0:10:58.21,Default,Shinomiya,0000,0000,0000,,We just have to go back now. Easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.21,0:11:00.72,Default,Mutsumi,0000,0000,0000,,It was my first time, but I had a lot of fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.67,0:11:04.58,Watamote-internal/narrator,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,But, little did they know...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.58,0:11:09.06,Watamote-internal/narrator,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,The traffic on the way back was an \Neven worse hell than when they came.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.85,0:11:13.61,Watamote-internal/narrator,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,So, by the time they arrived
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.61,0:11:15.61,Watamote-internal/narrator,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,for their closing celebration and Chri-Pa...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.89,0:11:19.39,Watamote-internal/narrator,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,all the boys had the energy level of corpses.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.23,0:11:21.56,sign_22941_233_Exhausted,text,0000,0000,0000,,Exhausted
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.73,0:11:24.51,Default,Nanashima,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.51,0:11:25.80,Default,Igarashi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.37,0:11:29.25,sign_23155_236_Closing_ceremony,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Closing Ceremony
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.25,0:11:32.07,Default,Nakano,0000,0000,0000,,That's what happens at your first Comiket.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.07,0:11:33.21,Default,Nakano,0000,0000,0000,,It takes a lot out of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.43,0:11:37.15,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it funny? I'm weaker \Nthan them, yet I feel great!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.15,0:11:39.21,Default,Nakano,0000,0000,0000,,Well that's because you had moe power.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.21,0:11:41.72,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,Moe energy! Got lots of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.92,0:11:43.09,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.33,0:11:46.89,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,There was a super cool Sebastian there, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.89,0:11:47.92,Default,Nakano,0000,0000,0000,,Got any pics?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.92,0:11:49.81,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,I don't, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.05,0:11:52.99,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh! If only I had taken one!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.99,0:11:54.81,Default,Nishina,0000,0000,0000,,I'm honored to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.92,0:12:00.77,Default,Nishina,0000,0000,0000,,How about taking one now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.53,0:12:06.21,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,No way! How? You're a student at this school?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.33,0:12:09.28,Default,Nishina,0000,0000,0000,,Yup. I'm in class 1-F.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.54,0:12:12.21,Watamote-internal/narrator,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,He's a—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.48,0:12:13.79,Default,Nishina,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Nishina Shima.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.79,0:12:15.21,Default,Nishina,0000,0000,0000,,Pleased to meet you, Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.21,0:12:16.82,Watamote-internal/narrator,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,He's a girl?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.84,0:12:21.88,Watamote-Eyecatch1,eye catch,0000,0000,0000,,Kiss Him, Not Me
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.88,0:12:26.89,Watamote-Eyecatch2,eye catch,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Kiss Him, Not Me
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.17,0:12:32.02,Default,Nanashima,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.53,0:12:34.58,Default,Nishina,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.58,0:12:35.83,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,Allow me to introduce you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.83,0:12:39.36,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,This is Nishina Shima-chan. She's \Na first year-like you, Shinomiya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.69,0:12:41.79,Default,Nanashima,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't know about her?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.79,0:12:44.18,Default,Shinomiya,0000,0000,0000,,There are six classes. I can't know them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.18,0:12:46.66,Default,Nanashima,0000,0000,0000,,More like, she was a girl all along?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.84,0:12:49.64,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,I thought she was a male \Ncosplayer at the winter Comiket,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.64,0:12:50.92,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,so this was a big shock.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.92,0:12:54.24,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,But after talking to her, it turns\N out we get along perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.24,0:12:55.17,Default,Nishina,0000,0000,0000,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.72,0:12:56.96,Default,Nanashima,0000,0000,0000,,So I guess that...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.86,0:12:59.21,Watamote-internal/narrator,Nanashima,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't count.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.42,0:13:00.61,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Nishina-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.16,0:13:02.46,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't gone home yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.74,0:13:04.42,Default,Girl 2,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing for New Year's?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.42,0:13:07.97,Default,Girl 2,0000,0000,0000,,When third semester starts, come\N hang out with us third-years again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.20,0:13:09.76,Default,Sporty girl,0000,0000,0000,,Nishina-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.76,0:13:12.40,Default,Sporty girl,0000,0000,0000,,Help us with the first match \Nof the new year again!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.40,0:13:14.56,Default,Other sporty girl,0000,0000,0000,,Not fair! We asked first.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.60,0:13:18.05,Watamote-internal/narrator,Nanashima,0000,0000,0000,,What's with this feeling of defeat?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.05,0:13:20.67,Watamote-internal/narrator,Shinomiya,0000,0000,0000,,You know what this is, don't \Nyou? The Takarazuka effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.67,0:13:22.24,Watamote-internal/narrator,Nanashima,0000,0000,0000,,Even if that is the case...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.24,0:13:23.69,Watamote-internal/narrator,Shinomiya,0000,0000,0000,,If we say anything, we lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.95,0:13:27.94,Default,Igarashi,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, it's definitely a surprise \Nto see you here in our school.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.94,0:13:29.94,Default,Igarashi,0000,0000,0000,,But it can't be just a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.94,0:13:34.21,Default,Nishina,0000,0000,0000,,Right. I had heard various rumors \Nabout Serinuma-senpai before Comiket,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.21,0:13:37.25,Default,Nishina,0000,0000,0000,,but meeting her there \Ntruly was a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.72,0:13:40.21,Default,Nishina,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed. It is too good to be true.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.81,0:13:43.22,Default,Nishina,0000,0000,0000,,A coincidence that's too good to be true...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.22,0:13:44.97,Default,Nishina,0000,0000,0000,,Some may call it fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.98,0:13:49.04,Default,Nishina,0000,0000,0000,,I want to value the bond we have.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.58,0:13:52.30,Default,Nishina,0000,0000,0000,,Please, allow me to invite you over to my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.66,0:13:55.43,Default,Nishina,0000,0000,0000,,We'll talk the night away about {\i1}Mirage Saga{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.70,0:13:58.69,Watamote-internal/narrator,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,Talk the night away about {\i0}Mirage Saga{\i1}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.88,0:14:00.19,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.19,0:14:01.44,Default,Nanashima,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.64,0:14:02.82,Default,Nanashima,0000,0000,0000,,We're going, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.82,0:14:06.05,Default,Nanashima,0000,0000,0000,,We also really want to all \Nnight about this {\i1}Mirage Saga{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.05,0:14:07.57,Default,Nanashima,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Shinomiya-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.84,0:14:11.48,Default,Shinomiya,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, you're right! Let's talk \Nuntil our throats are raw!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.48,0:14:13.02,Default,Igarashi,0000,0000,0000,,Then count me in, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.02,0:14:14.45,Default,Mutsumi,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds like it'll be fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.67,0:14:17.91,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,You're all interested in {\i1}Mirage Saga{\i0} now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.91,0:14:18.71,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.97,0:14:23.03,Default,Nanashima,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you know, now that \NI've gotten a taste for it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.03,0:14:24.59,Default,Shinomiya,0000,0000,0000,,You know it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.27,0:14:28.07,Default,Nishina,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, you're all more than welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.07,0:14:32.72,Default,Nishina,0000,0000,0000,,But I'd appreciate if you could \Nlisten to a small request of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.97,0:14:35.30,Watamote-internal/narrator,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,A-Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.82,0:14:39.30,Default,Maid,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home, Lady Shima.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.56,0:14:40.81,Default,Nishina,0000,0000,0000,,Please come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.06,0:14:42.62,Default,Nishina,0000,0000,0000,,My room is on the third floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.62,0:14:43.82,Watamote-internal/narrator,Nanashima,0000,0000,0000,,This girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.76,0:14:49.03,Watamote-internal/narrator,Nanashima,0000,0000,0000,,really feels like she popped \Nout of some 2D universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.03,0:14:50.82,Watamote-internal/narrator,Shinomiya,0000,0000,0000,,I get what you're trying to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.33,0:14:55.36,Default,Nishina,0000,0000,0000,,Take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.08,0:14:58.83,Default,Nishina,0000,0000,0000,,This room is mainly for my figure collection.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.83,0:15:01.84,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing! Amazing, amazing, amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.63,0:15:05.81,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,You have so many Shion figures!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.81,0:15:08.92,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,They're all so beautiful. \NEvery Shion is an angel!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.20,0:15:11.93,Default,Nishina,0000,0000,0000,,I bought this one from last \Nyear's Wonder Festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.94,0:15:13.37,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard of this one!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.37,0:15:15.07,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,This is by that super famous sculptor,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.07,0:15:17.99,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,and it's a completely \Nmade-to-order garage kit model!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.99,0:15:19.29,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,And the painting? Did you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.29,0:15:20.69,Default,Nishina,0000,0000,0000,,Yup. I did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.69,0:15:22.22,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,What? Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.22,0:15:24.24,Default,Boys,0000,0000,0000,,It's like a magic spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.25,0:15:23.45,sign_31991_329_Magic_Spell,text,0000,0000,0000,,Magic Spell
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.25,0:15:24.72,sign_31991_326_Iga,left,0000,0000,0000,,Iga
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.25,0:15:24.72,sign_31991_327_Shi,Mid,0000,0000,0000,,Shi
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.25,0:15:24.72,sign_31991_328_Nana,right,0000,0000,0000,,Nana
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.95,0:15:24.72,Watamote-overlap,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,Gorgeous!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.96,0:15:28.24,Default,Mutsumi,0000,0000,0000,,It's Tsuruga Castle. And \Nthis one's Hikone Castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.24,0:15:29.95,Default,Mutsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Did you make these, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.22,0:15:32.16,Default,Nishina,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, they're just plastic models, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.16,0:15:33.55,Default,Mutsumi,0000,0000,0000,,You're amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.55,0:15:35.24,Default,Nishina,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, not at all. I'm still learning.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.51,0:15:37.96,Watamote-internal/narrator,Nanashima,0000,0000,0000,,M-Mutsumi-san's down!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.57,0:15:40.18,Default,Nanashima,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.18,0:15:41.74,Default,Nanashima,0000,0000,0000,,She's a tough one!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.74,0:15:42.67,Default,Shinomiya,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.98,0:15:45.50,Watamote-internal/narrator,Igarashi,0000,0000,0000,,These two really get along.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.25,0:15:49.96,Default,Nishina,0000,0000,0000,,This is my costume room.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.96,0:15:52.56,Default,Nishina,0000,0000,0000,,These are all the clothes \NI've made up until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.56,0:15:55.12,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,You can make just about anything, \Ncan't you, Shima-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.12,0:15:56.32,Default,Nishina,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.32,0:16:00.62,Default,Nishina,0000,0000,0000,,The dress you made for \NShinomiya-kun was simply marvelous.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.62,0:16:02.01,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,How did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.01,0:16:03.33,Default,Nishina,0000,0000,0000,,I saw the play.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.33,0:16:05.43,Default,Nishina,0000,0000,0000,,Shinomiya-kun, you were very cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.43,0:16:06.94,Default,Shinomiya,0000,0000,0000,,Don't call me cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.16,0:16:10.07,Default,Nishina,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? But you really were cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.07,0:16:12.44,Default,Shinomiya,0000,0000,0000,,I told you not to say that! \NAre you making fun of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.44,0:16:13.78,Default,Nanashima,0000,0000,0000,,You tell her!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.07,0:16:15.66,Default,Nishina,0000,0000,0000,,I would never make fun of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.66,0:16:17.16,Default,Nishina,0000,0000,0000,,You were very beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.59,0:16:18.73,Default,Nishina,0000,0000,0000,,It was marvelous.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.86,0:16:21.60,Default,Shinomiya,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, thanks, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.60,0:16:23.44,Watamote-internal/narrator,Nanashima,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot, you're too easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.44,0:16:25.95,Default,Nanashima,0000,0000,0000,,I just told you to be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.95,0:16:26.67,Default,Igarashi,0000,0000,0000,,Easy, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.53,0:16:31.18,Watamote-internal/narrator,Igarashi,0000,0000,0000,,She is quite the smooth talker, however...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.90,0:16:35.26,Default,Nishina,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then. The room I want to \Nshow you the most is this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.76,0:16:42.42,Watamote-internal/narrator,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,Comics, novels,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.42,0:16:44.60,Watamote-internal/narrator,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,light novels, special bound\N books, limited books,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.60,0:16:46.06,Watamote-internal/narrator,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,doujinshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.06,0:16:48.11,Watamote-internal/narrator,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,These shelves are like \Nthe perfect BL collection!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.30,0:16:50.07,Watamote-internal/narrator,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.31,0:16:53.03,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,Can I see them? Can I?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.03,0:16:54.08,Default,Nishina,0000,0000,0000,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.93,0:16:58.26,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,It's a Zebra Stripe book.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.26,0:17:01.79,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,She's got all of them. Even \Nthe old ones that I don't have!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.79,0:17:04.13,Default,Nanashima,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that the author we \Nlined up for the other day?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.13,0:17:06.09,Default,Nishina,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. That's my circle.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.11,0:17:12.43,Default,Nishina,0000,0000,0000,,That's my circle. I draw manga, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.67,0:17:16.15,Default,Nanashina,0000,0000,0000,,You god damn liar! You can't \Nbe good at that many things!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.34,0:17:20.78,Default,Nanashima,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Serinuma?\N Why the pigeon impression?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.78,0:17:22.09,Default,Nanashima,0000,0000,0000,,Just lay into her!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.09,0:17:25.83,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious?! Are you \Nreally Yokojima-sensei?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.45,0:17:30.42,Default,Nishina,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Wait just a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.51,0:17:35.90,Default,Nishina,0000,0000,0000,,Will this convince you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.61,0:17:38.41,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,Are you some kind of god?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.87,0:17:40.79,Watamote-internal/narrator,Boys,0000,0000,0000,,Sh-She's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.79,0:17:42.74,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,I-I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.74,0:17:46.93,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,J-Just love Zebra Stripe's books.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.93,0:17:49.74,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,I-I always buy them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.74,0:17:53.47,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yokojima-sensei, \Nm-may I shake your hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.47,0:17:55.22,Default,Igarashi,0000,0000,0000,,Serinuma-san, calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.43,0:17:56.97,Default,Nishina,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.97,0:18:00.22,Default,Nishina,0000,0000,0000,,If it makes you happy, \NI'll draw for you anytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.36,0:18:12.30,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,Hold me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.30,0:18:15.36,Default,Nanashima,0000,0000,0000,,Cut it out! Get a hold of yourself, Serinuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.55,0:18:17.53,Default,Nanashima,0000,0000,0000,,I can draw just as good!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.53,0:18:19.27,Default,Nanashima,0000,0000,0000,,I got a 3 in art class!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.27,0:18:21.30,Default,Shinomiya,0000,0000,0000,,A 3 is a perfectly average grade!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.30,0:18:21.83,Default,Nanashima,0000,0000,0000,,Shut it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.28,0:18:23.66,Default,Nanashima,0000,0000,0000,,How's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.51,0:18:28.79,Watamote-internal/narrator,Nanashima,0000,0000,0000,,No good!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.13,0:18:33.11,Watamote-internal/narrator,Nanashima,0000,0000,0000,,She's rich, beautiful, smooth \Ntalking, able to do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.11,0:18:35.86,Watamote-internal/narrator,Nanashima,0000,0000,0000,,It's like she's a walking life hack!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.86,0:18:37.49,Watamote-internal/narrator,Nanashima,0000,0000,0000,,I can't beat her in any way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.49,0:18:38.58,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.35,0:18:41.10,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,This is Shion, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.11,0:18:43.17,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.17,0:18:44.66,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,Can I keep this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.66,0:18:46.73,Default,Nanashima,0000,0000,0000,,No way. I mean, it's garbage, isn't it? I suck.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.97,0:18:50.60,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true at all! It's \Nsuper cute! A great Shion!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.57,0:18:55.11,Default,Nanashima,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. Well, if you're happy with it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.32,0:18:56.77,Default,Shinomiya,0000,0000,0000,,How's mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.77,0:18:58.23,Default,Mutsumi,0000,0000,0000,,I tried drawing him, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.63,0:18:59.73,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,So cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.70,0:19:04.74,Watamote-internal/narrator,Nanashima,0000,0000,0000,,She's fine with anything as long as it's Shion.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.17,0:19:10.96,Default,Nishina,0000,0000,0000,,Now, do you all remember \Nhow I said I had a request?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.08,0:19:12.84,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.06,0:19:14.25,Default,Nishina,0000,0000,0000,,Come this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.05,0:19:18.09,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,What are we doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.37,0:19:20.61,Default,Nishina,0000,0000,0000,,I want to use you as models,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.61,0:19:21.84,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,since you're all here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.11,0:19:22.92,Default,all,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.92,0:19:24.64,Default,Nanashima,0000,0000,0000,,You just want to take our pictures?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.64,0:19:26.87,Default,Shinomiya,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by "since we're all here"?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.87,0:19:27.97,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,Shima-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.97,0:19:35.21,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,You mean, "since all these hot \Nguys are here together," right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.21,0:19:36.23,Default,Nishina,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.04,0:19:40.13,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,It's definitely good to go back to basics.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.13,0:19:42.70,Default,Nishina,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed. It seems they are \Nunaware of it themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.70,0:19:44.66,Default,Nishina,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe even some senpai-kouhai stuff here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.66,0:19:46.54,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,Simple is best. Simple is best!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.22,0:19:50.77,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Everyone, get into pairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.77,0:19:53.75,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,Igarashi-kun with Nanashima-kun. \NMutsumi-senpai with Shinomiya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.75,0:19:55.72,Default,Nanashima,0000,0000,0000,,What were you two discussing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.17,0:20:00.26,Default,Nishina,0000,0000,0000,,Looking good!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.66,0:20:03.04,Default,Nishina,0000,0000,0000,,Bring your faces closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.04,0:20:04.39,Default,Nishina,0000,0000,0000,,Lean into each other a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.43,0:20:07.95,Default,Nishina,0000,0000,0000,,Part your lips just a tad!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.95,0:20:09.14,Default,Nishina,0000,0000,0000,,Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.05,0:20:13.15,Default,Nishina,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.42,0:20:16.05,Default,Nishina,0000,0000,0000,,Now how about resting your \Nchin on his shoulder?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.05,0:20:16.77,Default,Mutsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.40,0:20:20.41,Default,Mutsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Shinomiya-kun, you use the \Nsame laundry detergent as me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.81,0:20:22.40,Default,Mutsumi,0000,0000,0000,,It smells good, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.40,0:20:24.38,Default,Shinomiya,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.17,0:20:27.20,Watamote-internal/narrator,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,This is heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.63,0:20:29.77,Default,Nishina,0000,0000,0000,,Next, please lay your head on the other's lap.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.79,0:20:32.31,Default,Nanashima,0000,0000,0000,,We're not gonna do that, idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.31,0:20:34.53,Default,Nishina,0000,0000,0000,,What? But you promised.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.53,0:20:36.91,Default,Igarashi,0000,0000,0000,,I think we've already done enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.91,0:20:38.13,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,Shima-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.63,0:20:40.93,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be faster if we \Nshow them how it's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.75,0:20:42.55,Default,Nishina,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.10,0:20:46.47,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,This is how you do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.66,0:20:47.97,sign_41713_450_Shi____Iga____Na,left,0000,0000,0000,,Shi    Iga    Nana    Mu
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.13,0:20:49.72,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,Gently lay your hand on their face,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.72,0:20:51.90,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,and subtly portray love, which is good.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.90,0:20:53.21,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, it's eye-catching.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.98,0:20:56.35,sign_41713_450_Shi____Iga____Na,left,0000,0000,0000,,Shi    Iga    Nana    Mu
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.24,0:20:56.35,Watamote-internal/narrator,Nanashima,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What is she talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.61,0:20:58.84,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,Then, bring your face\N closer to your partner's,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.84,0:21:00.32,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,and with your eyes open...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.38,0:21:07.57,Default,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! I-I'm sorry. I'm so embarrassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.30,0:21:11.54,Default,Nishina,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai, you're so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.04,0:21:26.55,sign_42858_460_Iga,left,0000,0000,0000,,Iga
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.04,0:21:26.55,sign_42833_461_Mu,left mid,0000,0000,0000,,Mu
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.04,0:21:26.55,sign_42833_462_Shi,right mid,0000,0000,0000,,Shi
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.04,0:21:26.55,sign_42833_463_Nana,right,0000,0000,0000,,Nana
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.33,0:21:36.53,Default,Nanashima,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck are you doing, Nishina?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.53,0:21:37.90,Default,Shinomiya,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Was that, just now...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.26,0:21:42.06,Default,Nanashima,0000,0000,0000,,Tone the practical jokes down!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.47,0:21:41.49,Watamote-overlap,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just now, I...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.25,0:21:43.90,Default,Nishina,0000,0000,0000,,That wasn't a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.15,0:21:47.89,Default,Nanashima,0000,0000,0000,,S-Serinuma! That one doesn't \Ncount, okay? It doesn't count!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.89,0:21:50.37,Default,Nanashima,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, idols do that stuff\N in music videos all the time!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.37,0:21:52.32,Default,Shinomiya,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah! I've seen that before!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.32,0:21:54.16,Default,Nishina,0000,0000,0000,,I said that wasn't a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.18,0:21:58.92,Default,Nishina,0000,0000,0000,,We'll have a problem if you \Ndon't start taking me seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.64,0:22:01.17,Default,Igarashi,0000,0000,0000,,This girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.75,0:22:05.97,Watamote-internal/narrator,Nakano,0000,0000,0000,,Serinuma Kae, 17 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.54,0:22:09.85,Watamote-internal/narrator,Nakano,0000,0000,0000,,Her first kiss is with a handsome girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.43,0:23:44.43,Watamote-internal/narrator,Nishina,0000,0000,0000,,Serinuma-senpai, you always make food \Nlook so delicious when you eat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.43,0:23:46.03,Watamote-internal/narrator,Nishina,0000,0000,0000,,And the way you eat is very pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.03,0:23:49.78,Watamote-internal/narrator,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Thank you!\NI like eating with you, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.78,0:23:51.84,Watamote-internal/narrator,Nishina,0000,0000,0000,,I can eat quite a bit, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.84,0:23:55.18,Watamote-internal/narrator,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,But you're not fat at all. \NDon't tell me you're on a diet.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.18,0:23:57.29,Watamote-internal/narrator,Nishina,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't done anything special.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.29,0:24:00.55,Watamote-internal/narrator,Nishina,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone in my family's the \Nsame way. Just good genes.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.55,0:24:02.36,Watamote-internal/narrator,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,My brother is actually skinny.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.36,0:24:04.78,Watamote-internal/narrator,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, maybe that's because when I was little,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.78,0:24:06.98,Watamote-internal/narrator,Kae,0000,0000,0000,,I used to steal my brother's\Ncandies and eat 'em all up!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.79,0:24:10.09,Watamote-Next-Ep-Title,title,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: \NBack to My Original Self! \NWhat Should I Do?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.79,0:24:10.09,Watamote-Look-Forward,red,0000,0000,0000,,Look forward to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.98,0:24:09.48,Watamote-internal/narrator,Nishina,0000,0000,0000,,When it comes down to it, \Nyou're pretty fond of your bro—
